        <abstract> 
<p>Thinks third edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> should advertise "additions and corrections", for the additions are important. They will add 30 pages to the book; there will also be a short historical sketch. Asks for some copies for friends.</p>  
<p>Also curious to know how <hi rend="italic">Journal of researches</hi> has sold. The new issue seemed a rash venture to him.</p> 
        </abstract>
